data.description: Nestled in the heart of Port Richey, this charming home offers a perfect blend of modern updates and convenient living. Recently refreshed, this gem boasts a new privacy fence that encloses a spacious backyard, providing a peaceful retreat for outdoor activities and relaxation. The interior features a contemporary design with stylish flooring and fixtures, creating a harmonious ambiance that welcomes you. Step inside to discover an intelligently designed layout that seamlessly connects various living spaces, providing ample room for both relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated, offering modern appliances and a delightful breakfast nook that bathes in natural light. This home ensures comfort with its well-appointed bedrooms, each providing a serene escape after a long day. The bathrooms have been tastefully updated, adding to the overall appeal. Notable features of this property include a new roof and air conditioning, both replaced in 2020, providing you with peace of mind and energy-efficient living. Additionally, the easy access to the Veteran's Expressway makes commuting a breeze, whether you're headed to work, beaches, or exploring the surrounding area. Step outside to your own private oasis, where the new privacy fence lets you fully enjoy the outdoor space. Whether you're dreaming of creating a vibrant garden, setting up a barbecue haven, or simply basking in the Florida sunshine, this backyard has endless possibilities. Conveniently located near local amenities, parks, dining, shopping, and entertainment options, 7639 Bramblewood Dr offers the best of both worlds – a tranquil residential setting with access to everything you need. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home. All measurements are deemed accurate by buyer to verify.
